Title: Ogudei's Lieutenants
Description:
There are two extremely powerful mogu spirits that the Alliance unearthed in their ineptitude.

These are choice targets for us, $c. If you kill them and collect each of their essences, we could make great progress on decoding the history of this strange ruin.
ObjectivesText: Collect Meng-do's Essence and Gen-li's Essence in the Ruins of Ogudei.
